472
00:26:42.583 --> 00:26:44.059
Yes, Father.

473
00:26:44.083 --> 00:26:46.708
Jefferson residence.
Rowley speaking.

474
00:26:46.791 --> 00:26:48.791
Rowley, I know you know it's me.

475
00:26:48.875 --> 00:26:51.833
I'm sorry. My mom and dad like
me to use good phone manners.

476
00:26:51.916 --> 00:26:53.750
Can you believe this snow?

477
00:26:53.833 --> 00:26:56.583
- I mean, how are you guys holding up?
- We're doing great.

478
00:26:56.666 --> 00:27:00.083
We made gingerbread cookies, and
now we're singing Christmas carols.

479
00:27:00.166 --> 00:27:03.750
Oh, want me to put you on
speakerphone so you can join us?

480
00:27:03.833 --> 00:27:04.875
No!

481
00:27:04.958 --> 00:27:06.500
I mean, no, thanks.

482
00:27:06.583 --> 00:27:09.166
Listen, Rowley, we need to make
sure we're on the same page

483
00:27:09.250 --> 00:27:11.375
