484
00:27:11.458 --> 00:27:12.791
You mean…

485
00:27:12.875 --> 00:27:14.000
Voldemort?

486
00:27:14.833 --> 00:27:17.791
What? That's
you-know-who, Rowley.

487
00:27:17.875 --> 00:27:19.958
I'm talking about the snowplow.

488
00:27:20.041 --> 00:27:22.208
Oh, yeah, that.

489
00:27:22.291 --> 00:27:26.375
Look, we won't be able to get our stuff
from that bin until it stops snowing.

490
00:27:26.458 --> 00:27:28.625
We're gonna have to lay low
and keep our mouths shut.

491
00:27:28.708 --> 00:27:30.083
Got it?

492
00:27:30.166 --> 00:27:32.708
- What do you mean?
- If someone beats us to that bin,

493
00:27:32.791 --> 00:27:34.434
we're gonna have to
get our story straight.

494
00:27:34.458 --> 00:27:37.708
So, if anyone comes by your house
and starts asking questions,

495
00:27:37.791 --> 00:27:40.416
you don't know how our
stuff got in there, okay?

496
00:27:40.500 --> 00:27:43.000
But why would someone
come to my house?

497
00:27:43.083 --> 00:27:45.166
There's something I
didn't tell you before.

498
00:27:45.750 --> 00:27:49.250
