stitched inside of my hat.

499
00:27:49.333 --> 00:27:51.416
Your name? That's bad.

500
00:27:51.500 --> 00:27:54.875
Listen, everything's gonna be
okay as long as you play dumb.

501
00:27:54.958 --> 00:27:57.166
You don't know anything
about anything.

502
00:27:57.250 --> 00:27:59.625
But lying would be naughty,

503
00:27:59.708 --> 00:28:01.083
and I'm nice!

504
00:28:01.166 --> 00:28:02.666
Rowley, I'm not
asking you to lie.

505
00:28:02.750 --> 00:28:04.583
