storm to punish us.

506
00:28:04.666 --> 00:28:07.333
- He knows. He knows!
- Rowley?

507
00:28:08.041 --> 00:28:09.841
Can you please calm down?

508
00:28:09.875 --> 00:28:11.500
Just focus on the
sound of my voice.

509
00:28:11.583 --> 00:28:14.083
