513
00:28:19.916 --> 00:28:21.000
- Stay on the line!
- 911!

514
00:28:27.041 --> 00:28:28.458
Rowley?

515
00:28:34.166 --> 00:28:37.166
Well, with the power out,
Rowley can't call the cops

516
00:28:37.250 --> 00:28:39.583
and spill his guts out
about the snowplow.

517
00:28:39.666 --> 00:28:43.083
And with the whole town snowed
under, nobody's getting to that bin.

518
00:28:43.166 --> 00:28:44.875
So, my secret's safe.

519
00:28:44.958 --> 00:28:45.958
At least for now.

520
00:28:46.041 --> 00:28:48.017
All I need to do is to make
it to Christmas morning

521
00:28:48.041 --> 00:28:50.041
without anyone in my
family catching on.

522
00:28:50.125 --> 00:28:52.916
Because in one week, I can call
that video game system mine.

523
00:28:53.000 --> 00:28:54.333
Okay.

524
00:28:54.416 --> 00:28:56.708
Three cases of water, 120
rolls of toilet paper,

525
00:28:56.791 --> 00:28:59.375
