633
00:34:16.875 --> 00:34:19.500
- The fuzz!
- But they know where you live.

634
00:34:19.583 --> 00:34:22.791
So if you rat them out for what
they did, you're both dead.

635
00:34:24.625 --> 00:34:26.958
Really, Rodrick? That's
what you came up with?

636
00:34:27.041 --> 00:34:30.625
Well, I, uh... I'm still
working out the details.

637
00:34:30.708 --> 00:34:34.708
